  87:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c **** /* TLS cert-upload / SSL-config sequence callbacks. Order mirrors
  88:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * a7677s_mqtt_state_t: START -> [CERT_CA -> CERT_CLIENT -> CERT_KEY]
  89:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * -> SSLCFG_CACERT -> SSLCFG_CLIENTCERT -> SSLCFG_CLIENTKEY
  90:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * -> SSLCFG_AUTHMODE -> SSLBIND -> ACCQ. Only entered when mqtt_use_ssl=1
  91:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * (see cb_mqtt_start()). Each *_prompt callback fires after the modem sends
