1026:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * response channel (see urc_poll() call site in a7677s_poll()):
1027:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  *   +CMQTTRXSTART: <idx>,<topic_total_len>,<payload_total_len>
1028:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  *   +CMQTTRXTOPIC: <idx>,<chunk_len>\r\n<chunk raw bytes>      (may repeat)
1029:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  *   +CMQTTRXPAYLOAD: <idx>,<chunk_len>\r\n<chunk raw bytes>    (may repeat)
1030:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  *   +CMQTTRXEND: <idx>
1031:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * per a76xx_at_cmd.md 18.4 — topic/payload chunks repeat as needed until
1032:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * their accumulated length reaches the total announced by RXSTART. Also
1033:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * catches +CMQTTCONNLOST:<idx>,<cause> (passive MQTT disconnect) and
1034:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * +CGEV: ME/NW PDN DEACT (network-level loss — treated as an implicit MQTT
1035:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * disconnect too, since MQTT cannot survive without the underlying PDN). */
