1295:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  *
1296:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * Key design: several MQTT commands return "OK" first, then a separate URC
1297:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/a76xx/a7677s.c ****  * line carries the real errcode (e.g. "+CMQTTSTART:0").  We set res_success
